','待定',1.0000,1,0,6,5,'2026-03-24 21:37:35','2026-03-24 21:41:38','{\"session_id\": \"9d82ca17-6b87-4250-8841-634219065084\", \"id_card\": \"42090219800101000A\", \"evidence_count\": 6, \"rounds_taken\": 0, \"final_conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"final_stance\": \"待定\", \"consensus_rate\": 1.0, \"is_consensus_reached\": true, \"history\": [{\"round_num\": 0, \"judgments\": [{\"agent_id\": \"agent_strict\", \"agent_role\": \"严格合规Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"不符合\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.9, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"依据严格合规判定准则，基础条件必须全部有明确满足的证据，排斥条件必须明确查无触发记录。本案中，虽然[BASIC_HARDSHIP_CATEGORY]、[BASIC_PERSON_ACTIVE]及[CALC_HISTORY_MONTHS]三项条件证据确凿且支持通过，但排斥条件[EXCL_SHAREHOLDER]、[EXCL_UNIT_INSURANCE]及[INFER_FISCAL_SUPPORT]均显示\'证据缺失\'（exec_status=\'no_data\'）。根据认知风格第2条，\'no_data\'的基础条件等同于条件未满足，且排斥条件无法排除即存在违规风险。因关键排斥性审查事项缺乏明确合规证据，无法确认申请人完全符合政策准入底线，故判定\'不符合\'。\", \"dissent_points\": [], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_lenient\", \"agent_role\": \"业务宽松Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.75, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"1. 核心条件满足：申请人具备‘大龄失业人员’认定类别，属于政策重点帮扶对象，且基础档案状态有效。2. 排斥条件解读：三项排斥条件（股东、单位参保、财政供养）均为‘no_data’状态，依据‘数据系统无记录即视为无违规’的经办惯例，这属于支持通过的利好信号，而非阻碍理由。3. 缴费核算：历史缴费记录连续（202601-202602），满足核算基础。综上，无明确排斥触发，建议认定符合。\", \"dissent_points\": [], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_explorer\", \"agent_role\": \"发散探索Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.45, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"已查证信息显示申请人基础身份有效（生存、系统有效），且持有有效的‘大龄失业人员’认定类别，历史缴费记录看似完整覆盖了202601-202602时段。然而，作为‘问题发现者’，我必须指出当前证据链存在严重的‘结构性缺失’。虽然三项核心排除性查询（股东、单位医保、财政供养）均返回‘no_data’，但这在真实业务场景中往往意味着核查未完成而非‘无风险’。特别是‘单位医保’和‘股东身份’是灵活就业补贴发放的‘一票否决’项，缺失这两项核查结果直接导致无法判断申请人是否真正符合‘灵活就业’的排他性定义。此外，历史缴费记录仅显示‘已领取’，未显示‘应发’与‘实发’的差额逻辑，且缺乏对应的就业登记时间线，无法排除‘就业与未就业并存’或‘身份切换’的隐患。\", \"dissent_points\": [\"核心排除项证据真空：三项关键的排除性证据（股东身份、单位医保、财政供养）状态均为‘no_data’。在补贴审核中，‘未查到数据’不等于‘不存在风险’，这种大面积的证据缺失导致无法排除申请人正在企业任职或享受财政供养的可能性，这与‘灵活就业’身份存在潜在冲突。\", \"就业状态时间线缺失：证据中仅有‘大龄失业人员’的认定结果，但缺乏‘就业登记’或‘失业登记’的具体时间戳。无法判断申请人在202601-202602期间是否处于‘灵活就业登记’有效期内，存在‘认定类别有效’但‘就业状态已变更’（如已就业但未同步）的时间线断裂风险。\", \"险种状态与基数异常预警缺失：证据未提供具体的缴费基数（pay_base）和险种变更日志（insurance_change_log）。考虑到当前时间为2026年，若申请人在此期间缴费基数突然大幅跳升，可能暗示其收入来源已不符合‘大龄失业’或‘灵活就业’的低收入特征，但当前证据无法支撑这一维度的风险排查。\"], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_empirical\", \"agent_role\": \"经验归纳Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.65, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"此案呈现出典型的【模式A：标准合规型】特征。申请人基础条件完备：持有有效的\'大龄失业人员\'就业困难认定，生命状态与系统状态正常，且历史缴费记录清晰（202601-202602），形成了连贯的缴费链条。然而，该模式成立的前提是必须排除\'隐性欺诈\'风险。目前证据面板显示，关于工商股东身份（EXCL_SHAREHOLDER）、单位医保缴费（EXCL_UNIT_INSURANCE）以及财政供养（INFER_FISCAL_SUPPORT）的三项关键排他性检查均为\'证据缺失\'。在经验审核中，这意味着无法确认申请人是否处于\'纸面合规但实际违规\'的状态。虽然核心数据指向符合，但缺失的风险阻断证据使得无法做出最终确切的\'符合\'判定。基于审慎原则，判定为数据缺失，需补全反欺诈核查。\", \"dissent_points\": [], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_auditor\", \"agent_role\": \"审计反驳Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.1, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"LLM 输出解析失败，原始片段: ```json\\n{\\n  \\\"agent_id\\\": \\\"audit_refutation_agent\\\",\\n  \\\"debate_round\\\": 0,\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"不符合\\\",\\n  \\\"confidence\\\": 0.70,\\n  \\\"r\", \"dissent_points\": [\"LLM 输出不是有效 JSON\"], \"key_finding\": \"解析失败\"}], \"total\": 5, \"majority_stance\": \"待定\", \"majority_count\": 5, \"consensus_rate\": 1.0, \"is_consensus_reached\": true}], \"policy_id\": \"POLICY_001\", \"status\": \"completed\", \"source_endpoint\": \"/api/debate_stream\", \"started_at\": \"2026-03-24T21:37:35\", \"completed_at\": \"2026-03-24T21:41:37\", \"summary\": {\"status\": \"completed\", \"policy_id\": \"POLICY_001\", \"source_endpoint\": \"/api/debate_stream\", \"final_conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"final_stance\": \"待定\", \"consensus_rate\": 1.0, \"is_consensus_reached\": true, \"rounds_taken\": 0, \"evidence_count\": 6, \"agent_count\": 5}, \"evidence\": [{\"evidence_id\": \"plan_basic_hardship_category\", \"rule_id\": \"BASIC_HARDSHIP_CATEGORY\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219800101000A\", \"target\": \"申请人是否具有有效的就业困难人员认定类别？\", \"category\": \"BASIC\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    hardship_category\\nFROM\\n    hardship_certification\\nWHERE\\n    id_card = \'42090219800101000A\'\\n    AND is_valid = \'1\'\\n    AND cancel_date IS NULL\\nORDER BY\\n    apply_date DESC\\nLIMIT 1;\", \"result_raw\": [{\"hardship_category\": \"大龄失业人员\"}], \"result_summary\": \"经核查，申请人当前持有“大龄失业人员”的就业困难人员认定类别。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": true, \"confidence\": 1.0, \"exec_status\": \"success\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T05:37:55\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_basic_person_active\", \"rule_id\": \"BASIC_PERSON_ACTIVE\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219800101000A\", \"target\": \"申请人是否处于存活且系统有效的基础状态？\", \"category\": \"BASIC\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    id_card,\\n    name,\\n    life_status,\\n    system_status\\nFROM\\n    person\\nWHERE\\n    id_card = \'42090219800101000A\'\\n    AND life_status = \'生存\'\\n    AND system_status = \'1\';\", \"result_raw\": [{\"id_card\": \"42090219800101000A\", \"name\": \"张完美\", \"life_status\": \"生存\", \"system_status\": \"1\"}], \"result_summary\": \"经核查，申请人张完美当前生命状态为生存，且系统状态码为1（通常代表有效），表明其处于存活且系统有效的基础状态。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": true, \"confidence\": 1.0, \"exec_status\": \"success\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T05:38:29\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_excl_shareholder\", \"rule_id\": \"EXCL_SHAREHOLDER\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219800101000A\", \"target\": \"申请人是否存在会触发排除的企业股东或工商主体身份？\", \"category\": \"EXCL\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    p.id_card,\\n    p.name,\\n    p.business_role,\\n    ci.company_name,\\n    cs.share_ratio,\\n    ci.company_type\\nFROM\\n    person p\\n    LEFT JOIN company_shareholder cs ON p.id_card = cs.id_card AND cs.is_valid = \'1\'\\n    LEFT JOIN company_info ci ON cs.company_id = ci.company_id AND ci.is_valid = \'1\'\\nWHERE\\n    p.id_card = \'42090219800101000A\'\\n    AND p.system_status = \'1\'\\n    AND (\\n        p.business_role IS NOT NULL\\n        OR cs.relation_id IS NOT NULL\\n    );\", \"result_raw\": [], \"result_summary\": \"数据库未返回任何记录。未能查证到当前事实。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": null, \"confidence\": 0.5, \"exec_status\": \"no_data\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T05:38:37\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_excl_unit_insurance\", \"rule_id\": \"EXCL_UNIT_INSURANCE\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219800101000A\", \"target\": \"申请期间是否存在单位缴纳医保记录，导致不满足灵活就业补贴条件？\", \"category\": \"EXCL\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    pay_month,\\n    insurer_status,\\n    company_id\\nFROM\\n    social_insurance_payment\\nWHERE\\n    id_card = \'42090219800101000A\'\\n    AND insurance_type = \'310\'\\n    AND insurer_status = \'101\'\\n    AND is_valid = \'1\'\\nORDER BY\\n    pay_month DESC;\", \"result_raw\": [], \"result_summary\": \"数据库未返回任何记录。未能查证到当前事实。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": null, \"confidence\": 0.5, \"exec_status\": \"no_data\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T05:39:01\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_infer_fiscal_support\", \"rule_id\": \"INFER_FISCAL_SUPPORT\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219800101000A\", \"target\": \"申请人是否存在财政供养或类似公共部门供养的高风险线索？\", \"category\": \"INFER\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    pi.id_card,\\n    ci.company_name,\\n    ci.company_type,\\n    pi.pay_month,\\n    pi.insurance_type,\\n    pi.insurer_status,\\n    pi.pay_base\\nFROM\\n    social_insurance_payment pi\\n    INNER JOIN company_info ci ON pi.company_id = ci.company_id\\nWHERE\\n    pi.id_card = \'42090219800101000A\'\\n    AND pi.is_valid = \'1\'\\n    AND ci.is_valid = \'1\'\\n    AND ci.company_type IN (\'机关单位\', \'事业单位\')\\nORDER BY\\n    pi.pay_month DESC;\", \"result_raw\": [], \"result_summary\": \"数据库未返回任何记录。未能查证到当前事实。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": null, \"confidence\": 0.5, \"exec_status\": \"no_data\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T05:39:09\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_calc_history_months\", \"rule_id\": \"CALC_HISTORY_MONTHS\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219800101000A\", \"target\": \"申请人历史已领取月份与当前缴费月份是否满足精算核算需要？\", \"category\": \"CALC\", \"sql\": \"SELECT \\n    id_card,\\n    GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT pay_month ORDER BY pay_month DESC SEPARATOR \',\') AS history_pay_months,\\n    MAX(pay_month) AS latest_pay_month,\\n    MIN(pay_month) AS earliest_pay_month,\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT pay_month) AS total_months_count\\nFROM \\n    social_insurance_payment\\nWHERE \\n    id_card = \'42090219800101000A\' \\n    AND is_valid = \'1\'\\nGROUP BY \\n    id_card;\", \"result_raw\": [{\"id_card\": \"42090219800101000A\", \"history_pay_months\": \"202602,202601\", \"latest_pay_month\": \"202602\", \"earliest_pay_month\": \"202601\", \"total_months_count\": 2}], \"result_summary\": \"经核查，申请人历史缴费记录包含202601至202602共计2个月，当前最新缴费月份为202602，数据完整覆盖了核算所需的连续时段。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": true, \"confidence\": 1.0, \"exec_status\": \"success\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T05:39:44\"}]}','2026-03-24 21:41:37'),('a6e9a396-9f91-4a8b-ba92-f3213f138d8a','42090219850505000B','POLICY_001','completed','/api/debate_stream','数据缺失','待定',1.0000,1,0,6,5,'2026-03-24 19:34:33','2026-03-24 19:39:54','{\"session_id\": \"a6e9a396-9f91-4a8b-ba92-f3213f138d8a\", \"id_card\": \"42090219850505000B\", \"evidence_count\": 6, \"rounds_taken\": 0, \"final_conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"final_stance\": \"待定\", \"consensus_rate\": 1.0, \"is_consensus_reached\": true, \"history\": [{\"round_num\": 0, \"judgments\": [{\"agent_id\": \"agent_strict\", \"agent_role\": \"严格合规Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.9, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"依据政策条文的刚性执行原则，申请人必须同时满足所有基础条件且不触发任何排斥条件。现有证据中：1. 基础条件[BASIC_001]、[BASIC_002]虽有满足证据，但不足以支撑整体通过；2. 关键排斥条件[EXCL_SHAREHOLDER]（股东身份排查）因系统异常导致证据缺失，无法确认申请人是否属于‘企业股东’等禁止申领人群；3. 排斥条件[EXCL_UNIT_INSURANCE]（单位参保）和[INFER_FISCAL_SUPPORT]（财政供养）均处于‘no_data’状态，无法排除违规风险；4. 核心计算条件[CALC_HISTORY_MONTHS]缺失缴费基数，无法完成精算核算。根据‘证据缺失即视为条件未满足’的判定准则，申请人因关键排斥条件无法核验及核心数据缺失，判定为不符合。\", \"dissent_points\": [], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_lenient\", \"agent_role\": \"业务宽松Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.65, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"\", \"dissent_points\": [], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_explorer\", \"agent_role\": \"发散探索Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"不符合\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.75, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"【已查证的正面信息】申请人李老板生命状态正常，且持有有效的\'家庭零就业人员\'就业困难认定类别，基础门槛看似满足。 【存在疑点与数据缺失】1. 核心排除条件\'工商股东身份\'查询失败（系统报错），这是重大的风险敞口，无法排除申请人经商的可能性。2. \'单位缴纳医保记录\'与\'财政供养\'查询结果均为\'no_data\'，属于证据链断裂而非\'无风险证明\'。3. 最关键的异常在于\'缴费基数缺失\'，这直接导致无法计算补贴金额。 【综合判断】在无法核实是否存在双重就业关系、是否经商、且核心计费参数缺失的情况下，申请处于高风险状态。特别是\'缴费基数缺失\'可能暗示数据源头存在录入错误或同步异常，不符合精准发放要求。\", \"dissent_points\": [\"核心计费参数\'缴费基数\'缺失，导致无法进行精算核算，这可能暗示社保缴费数据源头存在录入错误或同步异常，而非简单的数据为空。\", \"排除性规则\'工商股东身份\'查询出现技术性报错，这意味着系统无法排除申请人\'李老板\'是否存在经商办企业的违规情形，存在极大的合规隐患。\", \"申请人姓名为\'李老板\'，该名称具有强烈的个体工商户或私营企业主特征，与\'无工商股东记录\'的待验证状态形成直觉上的矛盾，需重点排查是否存在漏登或异地工商登记。\", \"当前缴费月份显示为\'202602\'（2026年2月），该时间点明显超出当前正常业务周期（假设当前为2024或2025年），存在数据预录入错误或系统时间线混乱的风险。\"], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_empirical\", \"agent_role\": \"经验归纳Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.65, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"此案与【模式E：数据矛盾型】高度相似。申请人虽然基础状态有效且持有就业困难认定，符合补贴的表面条件，但核心的排除性审查（工商股东、单位医保、财政供养）均出现系统异常或数据缺失。特别是\'card_EXCL_SHAREHOLDER\'出现系统保护性拦截，这在经验中往往暗示底层数据存在格式异常或严重冲突。此外，精算数据中缴费基数缺失，导致无法完成金额核算。综合判断，这不是一个标准的合规案例，而是一个典型的\'系统数据质量问题\'案例，必须转人工核实。\", \"dissent_points\": [], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_auditor\", \"agent_role\": \"审计反驳Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.1, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"LLM 输出解析失败，原始片段: ```json\\n{\\n  \\\"agent_id\\\": \\\"Audit_Refusal_Agent\\\",\\n  \\\"agent_role\\\": \\\"审计反驳Agent\\\",\\n  \\\"final_decision\\\": \\\"不符合\\\",\\n  \\\"confidence\\\": 0\", \"dissent_points\": [\"LLM 输出不是有效 JSON\"], \"key_finding\": \"解析失败\"}], \"total\": 5, \"majority_stance\": \"待定\", \"majority_count\": 5, \"consensus_rate\": 1.0, \"is_consensus_reached\": true}], \"policy_id\": \"POLICY_001\", \"status\": \"completed\", \"source_endpoint\": \"/api/debate_stream\", \"started_at\": \"2026-03-24T19:34:33\", \"completed_at\": \"2026-03-24T19:39:53\", \"summary\": {\"status\": \"completed\", \"policy_id\": \"POLICY_001\", \"source_endpoint\": \"/api/debate_stream\", \"final_conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"final_stance\": \"待定\", \"consensus_rate\": 1.0, \"is_consensus_reached\": true, \"rounds_taken\": 0, \"evidence_count\": 6, \"agent_count\": 5}, \"evidence\": [{\"evidence_id\": \"plan_basic_hardship_category\", \"rule_id\": \"BASIC_HARDSHIP_CATEGORY\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219850505000B\", \"target\": \"申请人是否具有有效的就业困难人员认定类别？\", \"category\": \"BASIC\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    hardship_category\\nFROM\\n    hardship_certification\\nWHERE\\n    id_card = \'42090219850505000B\'\\n    AND is_valid = \'1\'\\nORDER BY\\n    apply_date DESC\\nLIMIT 1;\", \"result_raw\": [{\"hardship_category\": \"家庭零就业人员\"}], \"result_summary\": \"已查实申请人当前持有有效的就业困难人员认定类别，具体为‘家庭零就业人员’。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": true, \"confidence\": 1.0, \"exec_status\": \"success\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T03:34:57\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_basic_person_active\", \"rule_id\": \"BASIC_PERSON_ACTIVE\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219850505000B\", \"target\": \"申请人是否处于存活且系统有效的基础状态？\", \"category\": \"BASIC\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    id_card,\\n    name,\\n    life_status,\\n    system_status\\nFROM\\n    person\\nWHERE\\n    id_card = \'42090219850505000B\'\\n    AND life_status = \'生存\'\\n    AND system_status = \'1\';\", \"result_raw\": [{\"id_card\": \"42090219850505000B\", \"name\": \"李老板\", \"life_status\": \"生存\", \"system_status\": \"1\"}], \"result_summary\": \"已查实申请人李老板当前生命状态为生存，且系统状态码为1（有效），表明其基础状态正常。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": true, \"confidence\": 1.0, \"exec_status\": \"success\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T03:35:06\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_excl_shareholder\", \"rule_id\": \"EXCL_SHAREHOLDER\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219850505000B\", \"target\": \"申请人是否存在会触发排除的企业股东或工商主体身份？\", \"category\": \"EXCL\", \"sql\": \"SQL 生成与执行链路遭受毁灭性破坏\", \"result_raw\": [], \"result_summary\": \"系统保护性拦截异常: Object of type Decimal is not JSON serializable\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": null, \"confidence\": 0.0, \"exec_status\": \"failed\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T03:35:21\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_excl_unit_insurance\", \"rule_id\": \"EXCL_UNIT_INSURANCE\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219850505000B\", \"target\": \"申请期间是否存在单位缴纳医保记录，导致不满足灵活就业补贴条件？\", \"category\": \"EXCL\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    id_card,\\n    pay_month,\\n    insurer_status,\\n    company_id\\nFROM\\n    social_insurance_payment\\nWHERE\\n    id_card = \'42090219850505000B\'\\n    AND insurance_type = \'310\'\\n    AND insurer_status = \'101\'\\n    AND is_valid = \'1\'\\nORDER BY\\n    pay_month DESC;\", \"result_raw\": [], \"result_summary\": \"数据库未返回任何记录。未能查证到当前事实。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": null, \"confidence\": 0.5, \"exec_status\": \"no_data\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T03:35:25\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_infer_fiscal_support\", \"rule_id\": \"INFER_FISCAL_SUPPORT\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219850505000B\", \"target\": \"申请人是否存在财政供养或类似公共部门供养的高风险线索？\", \"category\": \"INFER\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    sip.payment_id,\\n    sip.id_card,\\n    sip.company_id,\\n    ci.company_name,\\n    ci.company_type,\\n    sip.insurance_type,\\n    sip.pay_month,\\n    sip.insurer_status,\\n    sip.pay_base\\nFROM\\n    social_insurance_payment sip\\nINNER JOIN\\n    company_info ci ON sip.company_id = ci.company_id\\nWHERE\\n    sip.id_card = \'42090219850505000B\'\\n    AND sip.is_valid = \'1\'\\n    AND ci.is_valid = \'1\'\\n    AND sip.insurer_status = \'101\'\\n    AND ci.company_type IN (\'机关单位\', \'事业单位\')\\nORDER BY\\n    sip.pay_month DESC;\", \"result_raw\": [], \"result_summary\": \"数据库未返回任何记录。未能查证到当前事实。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": null, \"confidence\": 0.5, \"exec_status\": \"no_data\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T03:35:36\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_calc_history_months\", \"rule_id\": \"CALC_HISTORY_MONTHS\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219850505000B\", \"target\": \"申请人历史已领取月份与当前缴费月份是否满足精算核算需要？\", \"category\": \"CALC\", \"sql\": \"SELECT \\n    id_card,\\n    pay_month,\\n    insurance_type,\\n    insurer_status,\\n    pay_base\\nFROM \\n    social_insurance_payment\\nWHERE \\n    id_card = \'42090219850505000B\' \\n    AND is_valid = \'1\'\\nORDER BY \\n    pay_month DESC;\", \"result_raw\": [{\"id_card\": \"42090219850505000B\", \"pay_month\": \"202602\", \"insurance_type\": \"110\", \"insurer_status\": \"102\", \"pay_base\": null}], \"result_summary\": \"经核查，申请人当前缴费月份为202602，险种类型为110，参保状态为102，但缴费基数缺失，无法计算历史已领取月份与当前缴费月份的精算核算关系。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": null, \"confidence\": 1.0, \"exec_status\": \"success\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T03:36:30\"}]}','2026-03-24 19:39:53'),('ab49e030-36c0-446e-a1c0-86c8d84a2f61','42090219760310000D','POLICY_001','completed','/api/debate_stream','数据缺失','待定',1.0000,1,0,6,5,'2026-03-24 17:01:36','2026-03-24 17:06:17','{\"session_id\": \"ab49e030-36c0-446e-a1c0-86c8d84a2f61\", \"id_card\": \"42090219760310000D\", \"evidence_count\": 6, \"rounds_taken\": 0, \"final_conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"final_stance\": \"待定\", \"consensus_rate\": 1.0, \"is_consensus_reached\": true, \"history\": [{\"round_num\": 0, \"judgments\": [{\"agent_id\": \"agent_strict\", \"agent_role\": \"严格合规Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"不符合\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.9, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"依据政策条文，灵活就业社保补贴资格认定要求基础条件必须全部有明确满足的证据。现有证据显示：\\n1. 基础条件[BASIC_HARDSHIP_CATEGORY]（就业困难人员认定类别）状态为\'no_data\'，属于证据缺失，无法证实申请人具备申请资格的必要前提条件，该基础条件判定为未满足。\\n2. 排斥条件[EXCL_SHAREHOLDER]、[EXCL_UNIT_INSURANCE]、[INFER_FISCAL_SUPPORT]均为\'no_data\'，无法排除申请人存在违规领取补贴或不符合灵活就业状态的风险。\\n根据\'基础条件6项必须全部有明确满足的证据，缺任一即判不符合\'的原则，因核心认定类别证据缺失，直接判定不符合。\", \"dissent_points\": [], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_lenient\", \"agent_role\": \"业务宽松Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.65, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"基于业务实操视角，申请人基础信息有效（生存且系统正常），且历史领取记录与当前缴费月份核算清晰，无超期领取风险。虽然就业困难认定、股东身份、单位参保、财政供养等关键排斥条件均显示\'证据缺失\'，但依据\'法无禁止即可为\'的服务理念，排斥条件无数据触发（exec_status=\'no_data\'）应视为未触发排斥，这对申请人是利好。在无明确违规记录的前提下，不应因后台数据同步滞后或查证暂时空白而拒绝真实困难人员的申请。建议在后续环节补全就业困难认定证明，但当前节点倾向于通过。\", \"dissent_points\": [], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_explorer\", \"agent_role\": \"发散探索Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"不符合\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.75, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"已查证信息：申请人生命状态正常，且历史领取记录显示仅有202602单月记录。尚未核实信息：就业困难人员认定类别、工商股东身份、单位代缴医保记录、财政供养情况四项核心证据均显示\'no_data\'。存在疑点：在四项关键资格准入与排除条件证据完全缺失的情况下，现有的两项\'通过\'证据不足以支撑资格认定。特别是\'就业困难人员认定\'作为申请的前置条件，其缺失直接导致资格不成立。同时，\'单位缴纳医保\'数据的缺失无法排除申请人已实现单位就业的冲突可能。\", \"dissent_points\": [\"核心前置条件证据缺失：[card_BASIC_HARDSHIP_CATEGORY] 显示\'no_data\'，意味着无法确认申请人是否具备\'就业困难人员\'这一核心申请资格，根据政策逻辑，无认定即无资格，不能视为默认通过。\", \"排除性条款无法核验：[card_EXCL_SHAREHOLDER] 和 [card_EXCL_UNIT_INSURANCE] 均无数据。若申请人正在经营个体工商户或已由单位缴纳社保，则直接违反灵活就业补贴的排他性规定，当前数据盲区构成重大风险。\", \"数据完整性存疑：6项证据中有4项缺失，证据链完整度不足40%。在此情况下，[card_CALC_HISTORY_MONTHS] 显示的\'202602\'记录虽然逻辑自洽，但缺乏身份背景支撑，存在\'错误发放\'的历史遗留风险隐患。\", \"财政供养风险未排除：[card_INFER_FISCAL_SUPPORT] 数据缺失，无法排除申请人属于公务员或事业单位在编人员等违规申领群体。\"], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_empirical\", \"agent_role\": \"经验归纳Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.5, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"\", \"dissent_points\": [], \"key_finding\": \"\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_auditor\", \"agent_role\": \"审计反驳Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.7, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"作为审计反驳Agent，我认为该申请目前完全不符合审批通过的标准。核心依据如下：1. 基础条件存在致命缺失：\'就业困难人员认定类别\'(card_BASIC_HARDSHIP_CATEGORY)是申请补贴的前置资格条件，目前证据状态为\'no_data\'。根据审计准则，\'未查到记录\'不等于\'具备资格\'，缺乏必要的身份认定文件直接导致申请资格不成立。2. 排斥条件验证失效：虽然申请人处于存活状态(card_BASIC_PERSON_ACTIVE)，但三项关键的排斥性条件（工商股东、单位医保、财政供养）均显示为\'no_data\'。这种状态无法证明申请人\'不存在\'排斥情形，只能说明\'未发现\'，存在极大的合规风险敞口。3. 历史数据存在异常信号：card_CALC_HISTORY_MONTHS 显示历史已领取月份为202602，当前缴费月份也是202602，数据过于\'巧合\'且累计月数极少，这种\'完美\'的初始状态反而需要警惕是否存在新开户套取补贴或数据录入错误的风险。综上所述，在缺乏核心资质证明且排斥风险未排除的情况下，申请不应通过。\", \"dissent_points\": [\"基础资质证据链断裂：申请人未能提供\'就业困难人员认定\'的有效证明（证据返回no_data），缺乏这一前置条件，任何后续的补贴计算都缺乏合法性基础。\", \"排斥条件验证不足：对于\'无股东身份\'、\'无单位医保\'、\'无财政供养\'三项关键排斥条件，证据显示均为\'no_data\'。其他Agent若将此解读为\'符合条件\'即犯了\'诉诸无知\'的逻辑谬误，\'未发现违规\'不等于\'确实合规\'。\", \"数据完整性风险：六项证据中有四项为\'no_data\'，证据完整度极低。在此情况下强行判定，极易造成违规发放。\", \"历史核算数据存疑：历史领取月份与当前缴费月份完全重合（均为202602），这种\'零历史积累\'的完美状态在实际业务中占比极低，建议人工核实是否存在系统数据污染或欺诈申请风险。\"], \"key_finding\": \"\"}], \"total\": 5, \"majority_stance\": \"待定\", \"majority_count\": 5, \"consensus_rate\": 1.0, \"is_consensus_reached\": true}], \"status\": \"completed\", \"source_endpoint\": \"/api/debate_stream\", \"started_at\": \"2026-03-24T17:01:36\", \"completed_at\": \"2026-03-24T17:06:16\", \"summary\": {\"status\": \"completed\", \"source_endpoint\": \"/api/debate_stream\", \"final_conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"final_stance\": \"待定\", \"consensus_rate\": 1.0, \"is_consensus_reached\": true, \"rounds_taken\": 0, \"evidence_count\": 6, \"agent_count\": 5}, \"evidence\": [{\"evidence_id\": \"plan_basic_hardship_category\", \"rule_id\": \"BASIC_HARDSHIP_CATEGORY\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219760310000D\", \"target\": \"申请人是否具有有效的就业困难人员认定类别？\", \"category\": \"BASIC\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    hardship_category\\nFROM\\n    hardship_certification\\nWHERE\\n    id_card = \'42090219760310000D\'\\n    AND is_valid = \'1\'\\n    AND (cancel_date IS NULL OR cancel_date > CURDATE())\\nORDER BY\\n    apply_date DESC\\nLIMIT 1;\", \"result_raw\": [], \"result_summary\": \"数据库未返回任何记录。未能查证到当前事实。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": null, \"confidence\": 0.5, \"exec_status\": \"no_data\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T01:01:47\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_basic_person_active\", \"rule_id\": \"BASIC_PERSON_ACTIVE\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219760310000D\", \"target\": \"申请人是否处于存活且系统有效的基础状态？\", \"category\": \"BASIC\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    id_card,\\n    name,\\n    life_status,\\n    system_status\\nFROM\\n    person\\nWHERE\\n    id_card = \'42090219760310000D\'\\n    AND life_status = \'生存\'\\n    AND system_status = \'1\'\\nLIMIT 1;\", \"result_raw\": [{\"id_card\": \"42090219760310000D\", \"name\": \"赵争议\", \"life_status\": \"生存\", \"system_status\": \"1\"}], \"result_summary\": \"已查实申请人赵争议当前生命状态为“生存”，且系统状态码为“1”表示系统有效。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": true, \"confidence\": 1.0, \"exec_status\": \"success\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T01:01:57\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_excl_shareholder\", \"rule_id\": \"EXCL_SHAREHOLDER\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219760310000D\", \"target\": \"申请人是否存在会触发排除的企业股东或工商主体身份？\", \"category\": \"EXCL\", \"sql\": \"SELECT \\n    p.id_card,\\n    p.name,\\n    p.business_role,\\n    ci.company_name,\\n    ci.company_type,\\n    cs.share_ratio\\nFROM \\n    person p\\nLEFT JOIN \\n    company_shareholder cs ON p.id_card = cs.id_card AND cs.is_valid = \'1\'\\nLEFT JOIN \\n    company_info ci ON cs.company_id = ci.company_id AND ci.is_valid = \'1\'\\nWHERE \\n    p.id_card = \'42090219760310000D\' \\n    AND p.system_status = \'1\'\\n    AND (\\n        -- 情况1：人员主表直接标记为工商注册身份（法人或个体工商户）\\n        p.business_role IN (\'企业法人\', \'个体工商户\')\\n        -- 情况2：在有效企业中持有股份（股东身份）\\n        OR cs.relation_id IS NOT NULL\\n    );\", \"result_raw\": [], \"result_summary\": \"数据库未返回任何记录。未能查证到当前事实。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": null, \"confidence\": 0.5, \"exec_status\": \"no_data\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T01:02:33\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_excl_unit_insurance\", \"rule_id\": \"EXCL_UNIT_INSURANCE\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219760310000D\", \"target\": \"申请期间是否存在单位缴纳医保记录，导致不满足灵活就业补贴条件？\", \"category\": \"EXCL\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    id_card,\\n    pay_month,\\n    insurer_status,\\n    company_id\\nFROM\\n    social_insurance_payment\\nWHERE\\n    id_card = \'42090219760310000D\'\\n    AND insurance_type = \'310\'\\n    AND insurer_status = \'101\'\\n    AND is_valid = \'1\'\\nORDER BY\\n    pay_month DESC;\", \"result_raw\": [], \"result_summary\": \"数据库未返回任何记录。未能查证到当前事实。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": null, \"confidence\": 0.5, \"exec_status\": \"no_data\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T01:02:49\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_infer_fiscal_support\", \"rule_id\": \"INFER_FISCAL_SUPPORT\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219760310000D\", \"target\": \"申请人是否存在财政供养或类似公共部门供养的高风险线索？\", \"category\": \"INFER\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    si.id_card,\\n    si.pay_month,\\n    si.insurance_type,\\n    si.insurer_status,\\n    ci.company_id,\\n    ci.company_name,\\n    ci.company_type,\\n    CASE\\n        WHEN ci.company_type IN (\'机关单位\', \'事业单位\') THEN \'高风险：单位性质为机关/事业单位，存在财政供养嫌疑\'\\n        WHEN ci.company_type = \'社会团体\' THEN \'中风险：单位性质为社会团体，存在公共部门供养可能\'\\n        ELSE \'低风险\'\\n    END AS risk_clue_level\\nFROM\\n    social_insurance_payment si\\nINNER JOIN\\n    company_info ci ON si.company_id = ci.company_id\\nWHERE\\n    si.id_card = \'42090219760310000D\'\\n    AND si.is_valid = \'1\'\\n    AND ci.is_valid = \'1\'\\n    AND si.insurer_status = \'101\'\\n    AND ci.company_type IN (\'机关单位\', \'事业单位\', \'社会团体\')\\nORDER BY\\n    si.pay_month DESC;\", \"result_raw\": [], \"result_summary\": \"数据库未返回任何记录。未能查证到当前事实。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": null, \"confidence\": 0.5, \"exec_status\": \"no_data\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T01:02:58\"}, {\"evidence_id\": \"plan_calc_history_months\", \"rule_id\": \"CALC_HISTORY_MONTHS\", \"target_id_card\": \"42090219760310000D\", \"target\": \"申请人历史已领取月份与当前缴费月份是否满足精算核算需要？\", \"category\": \"CALC\", \"sql\": \"SELECT \\n    id_card,\\n    GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT pay_month ORDER BY pay_month ASC SEPARATOR \',\') AS history_pay_months,\\n    MAX(pay_month) AS current_pay_month,\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT pay_month) AS total_months\\nFROM \\n    social_insurance_payment\\nWHERE \\n    id_card = \'42090219760310000D\' \\n    AND is_valid = \'1\'\\nGROUP BY \\n    id_card;\", \"result_raw\": [{\"id_card\": \"42090219760310000D\", \"history_pay_months\": \"202602\", \"current_pay_month\": \"202602\", \"total_months\": 1}], \"result_summary\": \"经核查，申请人历史已领取月份为202602，当前缴费月份为202602，两者重合且累计核算总月数仅为1个月。\", \"time_range\": null, \"supports_conclusion\": true, \"confidence\": 1.0, \"exec_status\": \"success\", \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T01:03:19\"}]}','2026-03-24 17:06:16'),('b5cbcf8e-2f7d-4eb5-a77f-166c1ff49ece','42090219800101000A','POLICY_001','completed','/api/debate_stream','数据缺失','待定',1.0000,1,0,0,5,'2026-03-25 11:42:30','2026-03-25 11:43:49','{\"session_id\": \"b5cbcf8e-2f7d-4eb5-a77f-166c1ff49ece\", \"id_card\": \"42090219800101000A\", \"evidence_count\": 0, \"rounds_taken\": 0, \"final_conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"final_stance\": \"待定\", \"consensus_rate\": 1.0, \"is_consensus_reached\": true, \"history\": [{\"round_num\": 0, \"judgments\": [{\"agent_id\": \"agent_strict\", \"agent_role\": \"严格合规Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\": \"待定\", \"confidence\": 0.0, \"evidence_refs\": [], \"reasoning\": \"系统错误导致判断失败: \'EvidencePlanItem\' object has no attribute \'evidence_targets\'\", \"dissent_points\": [], \"key_finding\": \"系统调度异常\"}, {\"agent_id\": \"agent_lenient\", \"agent_role\": \"业务宽松Agent\", \"debate_round\": 0, \"conclusion\": \"数据缺失\", \"stance\